@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_raruxp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.08 * tmp + 0.83) / 0.05) / wp.exp(0.33))
    v1 = (wp.abs(tmp) / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.59) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.85)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.22 + v1 + 0.41)) + 0.90)
    v0 = wp.cos(0.14)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
